videos.description: On the fast break, Kansas' Devonte' Graham lobs it up to Jamari Traylor, who skies to the rim and dunks over a defender, leaving the broadcasters and the Jayhawks' bench in a state of shock.
videos.headline: The dunk that made Musburger yell 'Holy Toledo!'
